function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }

function roundAwayFromZero(value) { // Check if the value is halfway between two numbers if (Math.abs(value % 1) === 0.5) { // Round away from zero for numbers exactly halfway return value > 0 ? Math.ceil(value) : Math.floor(value); } // For all other values, standard rounding return Math.round(value); }
